import React from 'react';
import { View, Text, StyleSheet, TouchableOpacity, ScrollView } from 'react-native';
import { LinearGradient } from 'expo-linear-gradient';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { SafeAreaView } from 'react-native-safe-area-context';
import { StatusBar } from 'expo-status-bar';

const ServiceHeader = ({ title, icon, color, navigation }) => (
    <View style={styles.header}>
        <LinearGradient
            colors={[color, '#0277bd']} // Water blue gradient
            start={{ x: 0, y: 0 }}
            end={{ x: 1, y: 1 }}
            style={styles.headerBackground}
        />
        <SafeAreaView style={styles.headerContent}>
            <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => navigation.goBack()} style={styles.backButton}>
                <Ionicons name="arrow-back" size={24} color="#FFF" />
            </TouchableOpacity>
            <View style={styles.titleContainer}>
                <View style={[styles.iconContainer, { backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.2)' }]}>
                    <Ionicons name={icon} size={28} color="#FFF" />
                </View>
                <Text style={styles.headerTitle}>{title}</Text>
            </View>
        </SafeAreaView>
    </View>
);

export default function WaterScreen({ navigation }) {
    return (
        <View style={styles.container}>
            <StatusBar style="light" />
            <ServiceHeader
                title="Water Department"
                icon="water"
                color="#03A9F4"
                navigation={navigation}
            />

            <ScrollView contentContainerStyle={styles.scrollContent}>
                <View style={styles.card}>
                    <Text style={styles.cardTitle}>Water Bill Status</Text>
                    <View style={styles.statusRow}>
                        <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle" size={24} color="#4CAF50" />
                        <Text style={styles.statusText}>No Dues Pending</Text>
                    </View>
                    <Text style={styles.lastPaid}>Last Paid: â‚¹ 450.00 on 10 Feb 2026</Text>
                </View>

                {/* Functionality placeholders */}
                <TouchableOpacity style={styles.menuItem}>
                    <View style={[styles.menuIcon, { backgroundColor: '#E1F5FE' }]}>
                        <Ionicons name="document-text" size={22} color="#03A9F4" />
                    </View>
                    <Text style={styles.menuText}>View Current Bill</Text>
                    <Ionicons name="chevron-forward" size={20} color="#CCC" />
                </TouchableOpacity>

                <TouchableOpacity style={styles.menuItem}>
                    <View style={[styles.menuIcon, { backgroundColor: '#E1F5FE' }]}>
                        <Ionicons name="water-outline" size={22} color="#03A9F4" />
                    </View>
                    <Text style={styles.menuText}>Request Tanker</Text>
                    <Ionicons name="chevron-forward" size={20} color="#CCC" />
                </TouchableOpacity>
                <TouchableOpacity style={styles.menuItem}>
                    <View style={[styles.menuIcon, { backgroundColor: '#E1F5FE' }]}>
                        <Ionicons name="alert-circle-outline" size={22} color="#03A9F4" />
                    </View>
                    <Text style={styles.menuText}>Report Leakage</Text>
                    <Ionicons name="chevron-forward" size={20} color="#CCC" />
                </TouchableOpacity>

            </ScrollView>
        </View>
    );
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    container: { flex: 1, backgroundColor: '#F8F9FA' },
    header: {
        height: 180,
        width: '100%',
        justifyContent: 'flex-end',
        borderBottomLeftRadius: 30,
        borderBottomRightRadius: 30,
        overflow: 'hidden',
    },
    headerBackground: { ...StyleSheet.absoluteFillObject },
    headerContent: { padding: 20, paddingBottom: 30 },
    backButton: {
        marginBottom: 15,
        width: 40,
        height: 40,
        borderRadius: 20,
        backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.2)',
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
    },
    titleContainer: { flexDirection: 'row', alignItems: 'center' },
    iconContainer: { padding: 10, borderRadius: 12, marginRight: 15 },
    headerTitle: { fontSize: 24, fontWeight: 'bold', color: '#FFF' },
    scrollContent: { padding: 20, paddingTop: 25 },
    card: {
        backgroundColor: '#FFF',
        borderRadius: 20,
        padding: 20,
        marginBottom: 25,
        shadowColor: "#000",
        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
        shadowOpacity: 0.05,
        shadowRadius: 10,
        elevation: 3,
    },
    cardTitle: { fontSize: 16, color: '#666', fontWeight: '600', marginBottom: 15 },
    statusRow: { flexDirection: 'row', alignItems: 'center', marginBottom: 10 },
    statusText: { fontSize: 18, fontWeight: 'bold', marginLeft: 10, color: '#4CAF50' },
    lastPaid: { fontSize: 13, color: '#999' },
    menuItem: {
        flexDirection: 'row',
        alignItems: 'center',
        backgroundColor: '#FFF',
        padding: 15,
        borderRadius: 15,
        marginBottom: 10,
        shadowColor: "#000",
        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 1 },
        shadowOpacity: 0.05,
        elevation: 2
    },
    menuIcon: {
        width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 10, alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', marginRight: 15
    },
    menuText: { flex: 1, fontSize: 16, color: '#333', fontWeight: '500' }
});
